articles.title: Govt says 'absolutely no deception' in presentation of PH vaccine rollout ranking - CNN Philippines
articles.description: The government says there was nothing misleading in ranking the vaccination rollout of Southeast Asian nations in terms of total doses administered, instead of the percentage of inoculated citizens.
articles.content: Metro Manila (CNN Philippines, June 14) The government on Monday said there was nothing misleading in ranking the vaccination rollout of Southeast Asian nations in terms of total doses administered, … [+2047 chars]
